><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 =
0 1em 0;">Operators, investors, and the fintech-curious should all be able =
to learn a thing or two from Lithic. We&#8217;ll cover:&nbsp;</p><ul style=
